ned%20a%2010%20percent%20duty%20for%20Chinese%20goods%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20similarly%20over%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20spokeswoman%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20affirmed%20Friday%20the%20February%201%20imposition%20of%20these%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20have%20allowed%20an%20unprecedented%20invasion%20of%20illegal%20fentanyl%20that%20is%20killing%20American%20citizens%2C%20and%20also%20immigrants%20into%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20not%20commit%20to%20exemptions%20on%20sectors%2C%20and%20rejected%20warnings%20that%20this%20would%20spark%20a%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20three%20countries%2C%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20Friday%20that%20tariffs%20on%20oil%20and%20gas%20could%20arrive%20around%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%20we're%20going%20to%20put%20tariffs%20on%20chips%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20put%20tariffs%20on%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20specifying%20which%20countries%20he%20would%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20vowed%20to%20impose%20higher%20duties%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminum%2C%20and%20eventually%20copper%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20going%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20the%20European%20Union%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20bloc%20%26quot%3Bhas%20treated%20us%20so%20terribly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20vowed%20Friday%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20response%26quot%3B%20if%20Trump%20acted%2C%20while%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20said%20her%20government%20was%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20Trump's%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20not%20specified%20tools%20he%20would%20use%2C%20though%20analysts%20suggest%20he%20could%20tap%20emergency%20economi