ike%20replacement%20judgment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-tour-of-india-2025%2Fhow-can-an-out-and-out-bowler-replace-a-batter-harshit-ranas-concussion-substitution-sparks-controversy%2Farticleshow%2F117809271.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20To%20Present%20Her%20Record%208th%20Consecutive%20Budget%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20will%20present%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%20amid%20geopolitical%20uncertainties%20and%20an%20economic%20growth%20rate%20slowing%20to%20a%20four-year%20low.%20New%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20threat%20against%20India%20and%20other%20nations%20add%20to%20uncertainties.%20She%20will%20begin%20her%20Budget%20speech%20at%2011%20am.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20a%20huge%20expectation%20of%20tax%20cuts%2C%20particularly%20for%20the%20lower%20middle%20class%2C%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20invoked%20the%20Goddess%20of%20wealth%20for%20elevating%20the%20poor%20and%20middle%20class.%20%26quot%3BI%20pray%20to%20Goddess%20Lakshmi%20that%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20middle%20class%20sections%20in%20the%20country%20are%20blessed%20by%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20told%20reporters%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Union%20Budget's%20presentation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20may%20be%20concessions%20for%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20is%20pinning%20hope%20on%20a%20reduction%20in%20income%20tax%20rates%2C%20along%20with%20a%20hike%20in%20standard%20deduction.%20Under%20the%20old%20tax%20regime%2C%20the%20basic%20income%20exemption%20limit%20is%20set%20at%20Rs%202.50%20lakh%2C%20while%20for%20those%20opting%20for%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20the%20limit%20is%20fixed%20at%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20Economic%20Survey%20seeking%20financial%20inclusion%20for%20rural%20households%20and%20small%20businesses%20as%20a%20priority%20area%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20may%20announce%20easier%20access%20to%20credit%20through%20microfinance%20institutions%2C%20self-help%20groups%20and%20other%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20significant%20investment%20in%20infrastructure%20is%20needed%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%20to%20achieve%20India's%20development%20goals.%20While%20there%20are%20varying%20estimates%20on%20the%20exact%20amount%20needed%2C%20there%20is%20general%20agreement%20that%20current%20spending%20on%20infrastructure%20must%20increase%20to%20meet%20these%20goals.%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20may%20make%20some%20major%20announcements%20on%20this%20point.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERevisiting%20tariff%20structures%20to%20support%20domestic%20manufacturing%20and%20reduce%20dependency%20on%20imports%20while%20helping%20manage%20exchange%20rate%20pressures%20are%20likely.%20Government%20infrastructure%20spending%20has%20been%20crucial%20to%20India's%20strong%20growth%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Rs%2011.11%20lakh%20crore%20outlay%20for%20the%20current%20fiscal%20will%20likely%20fall%20short%20by%20one-fifth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20likelihood%20of%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20announcing%20policies%20and%20initiatives%20to%20accelerate%20progress%20in%20the%20field%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20a%20topic%20that%20also%20occupied%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20discussions%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20meeting%20in%20Davos%20recently.%20China's%20highly%20efficient%20yet%20pocket-friendly%20AI%20model%20DeepSeek%20has%20started%20a%20global%20race%20to%20develop%20better%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEconomists%20expect%20the%20Union%20Budget%20will%20unveil%20tariff%20reforms%20and%20consider%20a%20concessionary%20tax%20rate%20for%20new%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20India%2C%20both%20of%20which%20would%20address%20emerging%20global%20challenges%20but%20could%20have%20mixed%20implications%20for%20the%20domestic%20economy.%20Lower%20tariffs%2C%20for%20example%2C%20could%20hurt%20protected%20industries%2C%20but%20cut%20costs%20for%20manufacturers%20that%20use%20imported%20inputs.%20Low%20corporate%20taxes%20could%20limit%20room%20for%20funding%20programmes%20to%20boost%20consumption%2C%20but%20encourage%20investment%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20decision%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20US%20policies%20is%20some%20sort%20of%20corporate%20tax%20relief.%20With%20President%20Trump%20promising%20lower%20corporate%20taxes%20in%20the%20US%2C%20economists%20expect%20India%20and%20other%20markets%20will%20in%20turn%20be%20pressured%20to%20keep%20corporate%20taxes%20low%2C%20lest%20the%20US%20undercut%20them%20in%20attracting%20global%20manufacturers.%20India%20lowered%20its%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20sharply%20in%202019%20to%2022%20per%20cent%20from%2030%20per%20cent%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20spurring%20investment%2C%20although%20analysts%20say%20it%20has%20mainly%20just%20boosted%20corporate%20profit%20margins%20without%20spurring%20new%20investments%20or%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20analysts%20agree%20on%20one%20thing%20-%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20on%20the%20path%20of%20fiscal%20consolidation%2C%20with%20a%20projected%20fiscal%20deficit%20of%204.5%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20for%20fiscal%202026%20against%204.8%20per%20cent%20ending%20on%20March%2031%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738372200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F49jq3pg_nirmala-sitharaman_650x400_30_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-budget-2025-nirmala-sitharaman-to-present-her-record-8th-consecutive-budget-today-7606379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20will%20pre