earch%20has%20repeatedly%20shown%20that%20the%20plant%20extract%20bakuchiol%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10683784%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20many%20retinol-like%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Like%20retinol%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fstaying-healthy%2Fbakuchiol-does-it-make-skin-look-younger%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estimulate%20collagen%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20collagen%20is%20what%20supports%20and%20plumps%20the%20skin%2C%20thereby%20preventing%20it%20from%20sagging.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fradiantderm.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Dara%20Spearman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MD%2C%20a%20board-certified%20dermatologist%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fradiantderm.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadiant%20Dermatology%20Associates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bakuchiol%20is%20a%20great%20retinol%20alternative%20because%20it's%20a%20lot%20gentler%20on%20the%20skin%2C%20making%20it%20safe%20for%20those%20with%20sensitive%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kapoor%20and%20Chacon%2C%20bakuchiol%20can%20offer%20the%20following%20impressive%20benefits%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELess%20visible%20dark%20spots%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPreventing%20clogged%20pores%20by%20promoting%20cell%20turnover%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReducing%20fine%20lines%20and%20wrinkles%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jintegrativederm.org%2Farticle%2F38079-a-comprehensive-review-of-topical-bakuchiol-for-the-treatment-of-photoaging%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20bakuchiol%20is%20just%20as%20effective%20as%20retinol%20in%20terms%20of%20diminishing%20signs%20of%20aging%20on%20the%20skin.%20Another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbjd%2Farticle%2F180%2F2%2Fe45%2F6601602%3Fsearchresult%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D