owever%20you%20wear%20them%2C%20just%20do%20it%20with%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20these%20out%20in%20one%20of%20the%20brighter%20colors%20that%20leans%20towards%20a%20lilac.%20Most%20of%20my%20wardrobe%20is%20made%20up%20of%20neutrals%2C%20so%20I%20like%20to%20add%20pops%20of%20color%20with%20my%20shoes.%20I%20wore%20my%20boots%20with%20skinny%20jeans%20and%20midi%20dresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bc42eff-e589-4634-9f9e-4a315665e347%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20part%20about%20most%20UGG%20boots%20is%20they%20can%20get%20easily%20damaged%20and%20lose%20their%20visual%20appeal.%20Being%20made%20of%20suede%20makes%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20elements%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20relevant%20in%20the%20winter%20when%20snow%20and%20salt%20can%20stain%20your%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20great%20if%20there%20were%20Ultra%20Mini%20boots%20in%20other%20materials%20that%20were%20more%20waterproof.%20For%20now%2C%20you%20can%20protect%20your%20shoes%20by%20treating%20them%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-54731-20%26h%3D4ff5d5861f8fed1a24e9aac4c62ecc618e1fd3839a78ee6fb6a01db76619f8e1%26postID%3D627144c60f65d8170311c483%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fultra-mini-ugg-boots-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FUGG-Protector-Set-Natural-Size%252Fdp%252FB01IU8U99A%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUGG's%20shoe%20protector%20spray%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20any%20suede-specific%20waterproofing%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20with%20UGGs%20is%20they%20don't%20have%20much%20arch%20support.%20As%20great%20as%20they%20are%2C%20I've%20never%20found%20the%20boots%20to%20be%20good%20for%20walking%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257c59bf3-a6cc-43d3-9c0a-5217f073b9a1%5C