2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftheyre-the-ones-who-wronged-us-freed-palestinian-prisoner-zakaria-zubeidi-rebukes-uk-and-us-over-harm-theyve-caused-13300393%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Riots%3A%20Court%20Pulls%20Up%20Cop%20For%20Failing%20To%20Probe%20Ex%20MLA's%20Role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20local%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20registration%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20officer%20for%20alleged%20hate%20crime%20during%20the%20February%202020%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20city's%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20deprecated%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20investigating%20officer%20(IO)%20for%20failing%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20alleged%20role%20of%20former%20MLA%20Kapil%20Mishra%20in%20the%20rioting%20incident%20connected%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20saying%20he%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20allegations%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudicial%20Magistrate%20Udbhav%20Kumar%20Jain%20was%20hearing%20an%20application%20under%20Section%20156%20(3)%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%2C%20seeking%20the%20court's%20directions%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the-then%20Jyoti%20Nagar%20SHO%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%20under%20this%20section%20can%20be%20exercised%20by%20the%20magistrate%20to%20direct%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20in%20respect%20of%20a%20cognisable%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%2C%20one%20Mohammed%20Wasim%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20among%20five%20people%20allegedly%20assaulted%20and%20forced%20to%20sing%20the%20national%20anthem%20during%20the%20communal%20riots%20on%20February%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clip%20that%20had%20become%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20purported%20to%20show%20five%20Muslim%20men%20being%20beaten%20up%20by%20policemen%20and%20forced%20to%20sing%20the%20national%20anthem%20and%20%26quot%3BVande%20Mataram%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20national%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20dated%20January%2018%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20the%20SHO%20police%20station%20Jyoti%20Nagar%2C%20Tomar%20(complete%20name%20with%20post%20not%20provided)%20and%20other%20unknown%20police%20officials%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20the%20complainant%20or%20victim%20and%20they%20cannot%20be%20protected%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20sanction%20as%20alleged%20offences%20committed%20by%20them%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20have%20been%20committed%20while%20acting%20or%20purporting%20to%20act%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20their%20official%20duty.%26quot%3B%20It%20directed%20that%20an%20FIR%20be%20registered%20against%20the-then%20SHO%20under%20sections%20295%20A%20(deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20class%20by%20insulting%20its%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%2C%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20342%20(wrongful%20confinement)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20SHO%20is%20directed%20to%20depute%20a%20responsible%20officer%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20inspector%20to%20conduct%20investigation%20in%20the%20present%20matter%20and%20role%20of%20other%20unknown%20police%20officials%20involved%20in%20the%20commission%20of%20alleged%20offences%20can%20be%20ascertained%20during%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20an%20action%20taken%20report%20had%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20IO%20in%20the%20matter%20that%20merely%20denied%20the%20complainant's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20action%20taken%20report%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20substantive%20steps%20that%20had%20been%20taken%20for%20conducting%20a%20preliminary%20inquiry%20and%20remained%20silent%20regarding%20the%20CCTV%20camera%20footage%20of%20the%20alleged%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThus%2C%20inquiry%20pertaining%20to%20alleged%20acts%20or%20offences%20against%20the%20complainant%20has%20not%20been%20conducted%20properly.%26quot%3B%20The%20also%20court%20noted%20Wasim's%20claim%20about%20identifying%20Mishra%20as%20leading%20the%20riotous%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20complainant%20saw%20that%20the%20personnel%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20were%20fully%20supporting%20the%20alleged%20accused%20Kapil%20Mishra.%20Policemen%20were%20also%20pelting%20stones%20on%20the%20Muslims%2C%20and%20firing%20bullets.%20Due%20to%20the%20above%20attack%2C%20the%20protesters%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20escaped%20from%20there%20to%20save%20their%20lives%20and%20thereafter%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20rioters%20led%20by%20Kapil%20Mishra%20also%20went%20towards%20Chand%20Bagh%20shouting%20slogans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20allegations%20against%20Mishra%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BIO%20was%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20police%20officials%20and%20either%20he%20failed%20to%20make%20inquiry%20against%20the%20alleged%20accused%20No%203%20(Mishra)%20or%20he%20tried%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20said%20accused%20and%20the%20action%20taken%20report%20was%20completely%20silent%20qua%20him%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20guarantees%20equal%20protection%20of%20law%20and%20equality%20before%20law%20and%20no%20citizen%20of%20India%20enjoys%20any%20special%20treatment%20from%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20The%20alleged%20accused%20No%203%20is%20in%20public%20eyes%20and%20is%20prone%20to%20more%20scrutiny%3B%20such%20persons%20in%20the%20society%20direct%20the%20course%20or%20mood%20of%20the%20public%20at%20large%20and%20thus%2C%20responsible%20behaviour%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20expected%20from%20such%20persons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20directed%20the%20complainant%20to%20approach%20the%20special%20court%20which%20was%20competent%20to%20try%20offences%20against%20former%20or%20sitting%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20July%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20transferred%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20death%20of%20a%2023-year-old%20man%20who%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20being%20purportedly%20assaulted%20and%20forced%20to%20sing%20the%20national%20anthem%20during%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738347960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fad5q4r98_kapil-mishra-_625x300_19_April_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-riots-court-pulls-up-cop-for-failing-to-probe-ex-mla-kapil-mishra-role-7607084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20local%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20registration%20of%20an%20FIR%20against%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20officer%20for%20alleged%20hate%20crime%20during%20the%20February%202020%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20city's%20northeast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCheating...%26quot%3B%3A%20Concussion%20Substitution%20Sees%20Rana's%20Entry%2C%20Internet%20Reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETalented%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harshit%20Rana%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115601-harshit-rana-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarshit%20Rana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20played%20two%20Tests%2C%20quite%20surprisingly%20made%20a%20surprise%20entry%20into%20the%20India%20playing%20XI%20in%20the%20fourth%20T20I%20against%20England%20in%20Pune%20on%20Frid