tes%2C%20%26quot%3BFlat%20owners%20renting%20to%20bachelors%20(boys%20or%20girls)%20must%20ensure%20submission%20of%20detailed%20information%2C%20including%20addresses%20and%20approvals%20from%20family%20members.%20And%20if%20bachelors%20are%20cohabiting%20with%20members%20of%20the%20opposite%20gender%2C%20they%20must%20submit%20either%20a%20marriage%20certificate%20or%20a%20formal%20approval%20letter%20from%20their%20family.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThese%20measures%20are%20implemented%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20safety%2C%20security%2C%20and%20maintaining%20harmony%20in%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20mentioned%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20staff%2C%20on%20the%20conditions%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20good%20decision%20to%20avoid%20the%20nuisance%20created%20by%20the%20bachelors%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBachelors%20provide%20fake%20certificates%20of%20their%20parents%20and%20on%20that%20basis%20they%20become%20tenants.%20And%20after%20some%20time%20some%20mishaps%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20a%20good%20decision%2C%20because%20it%20will%20stop%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20nuisance%20in%20the%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20LLB%20student%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20society%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20also%20focus%20on%20the%20security%20checks%20and%20give%20warnings%20to%20those%20who%20create%20nuisance%20at%20night.%20It%20will%20reduce%20unnecessary%20nuisance%20created%20by%20some%20tenants%20and%20would%20also%20not%20impact%20others%2C%20those%20who%20are%20living%20peacefully.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20various%20incidents%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%20past.%20I%20live%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20comply%20with%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%2C%20I%20have%20no%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20another%20student%20who%20lives%20in%20Tower%203%20of%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20PTI%2C%20Kushwaha%20s