20to%20resort%20to%20makeshift%20solutions%20to%20keep%20the%20devices%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20its%20current%20wireless%20communication%20system%20has%20exceeded%20its%20lifespan%20but%20despite%20assurances%20of%20digital%20wireless%20sets%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20the%20department%20has%20not%20received%20any.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Motorola%20wireless%20sets%2C%20operating%20on%20800%20MHz%20frequency%2C%20were%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20for%2010-12%20years.%20The%20system%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20used%20for%2024%20years%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manufacturer%20provided%20service%20maintenance%20until%202015%2C%20but%20the%20sets%20have%20since%20been%20left%20to%20function%20without%20proper%20technical%20support.%20Issues%20such%20as%20quick%20battery%20drainage%2C%20unclear%20voice%20transmission%20and%20disrupted%20connectivity%20have%20become%20a%20concern%20for%20the%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20(existing)%20wireless%20sets%20are%20several%20years%20old.%20The%20sound%20clarity%20is%20poor%20and%20there%20is%20constant%20crackling%20noise.%20I've%20heard%20that%20training%20for%20new%20sets%20has%20been%20planned%2C%26quot%3B%20Constable%20Pramod%20Soni%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnPolice%20said%20they%20often%20need%20to%20resort%20to%20temporary%20solutions%20to%20keep%20their%20devices%20intact%2C%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20their%20duties.%20They%20often%20use%20thick%20rubber%20bands%20or%20attempt%20quick%20fixes%20to%20deal%20with%20broken%20components.%20In%20areas%20where%20the%20transmission%20signal%20is%20weak%2C%20cops%20often%20struggle%20to%20communicate%20effectively%2C%20repeatedly%20saying%20%26quot%3Bhello%2C%20hello%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20challenge%20increases%20in%20situations%20involving%20law%20and%20order.%20These%20sets%20either%20fail%20to%20transmit%20urgent%20messages%20or%20cannot%20handle%20the%20communication%20load%2C%20leaving%20officers%20in%20a%20fix.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20version%20is%20very%20old.%20The%20voice%20is%20unclear%2C%20and%20there%20are%20multiple%20black%20spots%20where%20the%20range%20is%20inadequate.%20We%20need%20updated%20versions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sub-Inspector%20Narendra%20Chaudhary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20six%20tenders%20being%20issued%20for%20new%20wireless%20sets%2C%20the%20equipment%20are%20yet%20to%20reach%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20officers%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20seen%20the%20new%20sets%20yet.%20The%20police%20department%20must%20be%20making%20arrangements%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20know%20when%20they%20will%20reach%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Sub-Inspector%20Ram%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20police%20officers%20said%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20upgrade%20the%20communication%20system.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWireless%20systems%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20police%20operations%2C%20whether%20for%20VVIP%20duty%20or%20law-and-order%20maintenance.%20We%20are%20adopting%20the%20latest%20technology%20and%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20new%20system%20by%20next%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhopal%20Police%20Commissioner%20Hari%20Narayan%20Chari%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20new%20devices%20will%20have%20features%20like%20live%20location%20tracking%20(unlike%20in%20the%20case%20of%20older%20sets%2C%20officers%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20false%20locations%2C%20as%20the%20new%20sets%20will%20function%20like%20mobile%20phones%20with%20live%20location%20tracking)%2C%20remote%20deactivation%20(if%20a%20wireless%20set%20is%20lost%2C%20it%20can%20be%20remotely%20disabled%20from%20the%20control%20room%2C%20to%20prevent%20unauthorised%20people%20from%20eavesdropping%20on%20police%20communications)%2C%20enhanced%20clarity%20(the%20voice%20quality%20will%20be%20comparable%20to%20mobile%20phones)%2C%20and%20encrypted%20communication%20(the%20digital%20sets%20will%20feature%20encrypted%20coding%2C%20ensuring%20that%20unauthorised%20users%20cannot%20tap%20into%20police%20conversations).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20cases%20in%20the%20past%20where%20officers%20reported%20being%20in%20one%20location%20while%20they%20were%20actually%20elsewhere.%20The%20new%20system%20will%20improve%20supervision%20and%20modernise%20police%20operations.%20Such%20advancements%20should%20be%20welcomed%2C%26quot%3B%20Retired%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Shailendra%20Shrivastava%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20new%20set%20of%20devices%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20distributed%20across%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20force%2C%20covering%20Inspector%20Generals%20to%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspectors.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20to%20policemen%20linked%20to%20emergency%20response%20teams%20such%20as%20Dial%20100%2C%20traffic%20cops%20and%20beat%20in-charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738339680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Flpt9e248_bhopal-wireless-police_625x300_31_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhopal-police-stuck-with-old-wireless-sets-wait-for-digital-devices-drags-on-7606220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bhopal%20Police's%20ability%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20jobs%20are%20being%20hindered%20by%20outdated%20analog%20wireless%20communication%20systems%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20resort%20to%20makeshift%20solutions%20to%20keep%20the%20devices%20functional.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhopal-police-stuck-with-old-wireless-sets-wait-for-digital-devices-drags-on-7606220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Epack%20Durable%20Q3FY2