%20is%20so%20isolated%20that%20the%20closest%20humans%20are%20often%20astronauts%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station.%20It%20is%20also%20designated%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98spaceship%20graveyard%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20organisations%20deliberately%20crash%20their%20old%20satellites%20and%20spacecraft%20to%20ensure%20safe%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20journey%20is%20part%20of%20Navika%20Sagar%20Parikrama%20II%2C%20an%20Indian%20Navy%20initiative%20promoting%20ocean%20exploration%20and%20scientific%20research.%20Notably%2C%20the%20passage%20through%20these%20isolated%20waters%20was%20completed%20entirely%20under%20sail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20has%20this%20initiative%20contributed%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20collected%20water%20samples%20from%20Point%20Nemo%20for%20analysis%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Oceanography%2C%20contributing%20to%20marine%20biodiversity%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20acknowledged%20their%20achievement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20stating%3A%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9C%23INSVTarini%20charts%20through%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20isolated%20waters!%20Lt%20Cdr%20Dilna%20K%20%26amp%3B%20Lt%20Cdr%20Roopa%20A%20cross%20Point%20Nemo%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Oceanic%20Pole%20of%20Inaccessibility.%20A%20testament%20to%20resilience%2C%20courage%20%26amp%3B%20the%20spirit%20of%20adventure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C